{% comment %}
  Free Gift Engine — cart app block (Phase 5a SKELETON).
  Place in the cart drawer / cart page via the theme editor. Markup is intentionally minimal:
  the perception UI (progress widget, gift chooser, decline checkbox, toasts), the storefront JS
  that subscribes to AJAX cart events, calls /validate, reconciles gift lines, and applies the
  discount code are all Phase 5b. This block only renders the mount point + config seams.

  The widget NEVER sets prices (the minted code + Shopify discount do) and NEVER trusts client
  state for eligibility (the server recomputes in /validate).
{% endcomment %}

<div
  class="fge-app-block"
  data-fge-app-block
  data-proxy-path="/apps/free-gift/validate"
  data-presentment-currency="{{ cart.currency.iso_code }}"
  data-country="{{ localization.country.iso_code }}"
  hidden
>
  {% comment %} 5b renders the tier/progress widget, the "Choose your free gift" chooser, and the
  "Add my free gift" decline checkbox here, and mounts assets/free-gift.js. {% endcomment %}
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Free Gift",
  "target": "section",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
